{"tid":1382652,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不要現金 不要現金券 一齊食餐飯！！！！！","createTime":"2019-07-29T13:54:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T11:46:06.000Z","uid":220864,"like":139,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"afe4be7359c6fc861a616cb740997c94dc34faad","tid":1382652,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:54:21.000Z","msg":"我知香港好多好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係唔該你地記住一樣野<br />\n你比錢或者比現金券<br />\n比人影到<br />\n會話我地係收左錢出嚟<br />\n呢個係水洗都唔清<br />\n<br />\n所以希望大家<br />\n一齊食餐飯<br />\n或者買完裝早小小拎去前線分<br />\n好過你私底下比現金類嘅野我地<br />\n<br />\n希望大家明白<br />\n同好感謝大家一番好意<br />\nI love Hong Kong&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2e3a721088d2a515e7fb4986f078ef5cb1bc96","tid":1382652,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:54:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d62cf51b0b4ebcf5d12ea31ff0d3b02c7592db4d","tid":1382652,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:54:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e3d75207853a9a333a421d9830cfdf3caacea10","tid":1382652,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:54:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e58f8c1e9aa608d36e6859dabcf8ed7fc33e9ce","tid":1382652,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:55:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d20580f9d964991170f45d6b9d1e15471a0d5ce1","tid":1382652,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:55:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9bffbfcba0f4556f2c3a9f09fc57690ba1dded6","tid":1382652,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:55:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b2205c2d67dc7c899cc1a60742fedb66ac11efee","t